==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Autotypography
<hw>Au`to*ty*pog"ra*phy</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<ety>[<ets>Auto-</ets> + <ets>typography</ets>.]</ety> <def>A process
resembling ⟦ldquo⟧nature printing,⟦rdquo⟧ by which drawings executed on
gelatin are impressed into a soft metal plate, from which the printing
is done as from copperplate.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Autotypy</ent>⟦br⟧
